{{outlet}}
<h3>{{model.name}} Rover</h3>
<br>
<img id="rover-portrait" src="assets/images/{{model.portrait}}">
<br>
<p id="bio"><Strong>Biography</Strong>: The {{model.name}} rover was launched on {{model.launchDate}} by NASA.
It arrived at mars after months of travel and successfully landed on {{model.landingDate}}.
It's mission is currently {{model.status}} and has taken {{model.totalPhotos}} photos in its illustrious extra-planetary career.
{{model.name}}'s last batch of images were taken on {{model.maxDate}} which is Sol {{model.maxSol}}
(A Sol is a martian day equivalent to 24 hours, 39 minutes, and 35.244 seconds.)</p>

<h4>Cameras on the {{model.name}} rover</h4>
<ol>
    {{#each model.cameras as |camera|}}
       <li> {{camera.fullName}}</li>

    {{/each}}
</ol>

<h4 class="btn-primary btn-block" {{action "open"}}>
    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-camera"></span>
    &nbsp;Search Rover Photos&nbsp;
    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-camera"></span>
</h4>

{{if isShowingModal}}
{{#modal-dialog close="close" clickOutsideToClose=true}}
    <div class="image-modal">
        <h3>Select a date for {{model.name}}'s images.</h3>
        <label id="pikaday-modal-picker">
        {{pikaday-input theme="dark-theme" format="YYYY-MM-DD" placeholder="Select An Earth Date" minDate=model.landingDate maxDate=model.maxDate}}
        </label>
        <!--TODO: Make this post to the Rail API, check for saved data on that date for that rover, and if not then make request of NASA-->
        <label class="btn-primary" {{action}}></label>
    </div>
{{/modal-dialog}}

